ssets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇到我眼都突埋<br />\n同事話佢地見慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T05:52:03.000Z","msg":"咁都未炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同事住開青山？"},{"pid":"ac77668f4ba228a6eabde0576fcf93a6f61a366d","tid":2409780,"uid":349661,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T05:53:15.000Z","msg":"痴撚線 個老細有房坐？<br />\n點會可以同佢生存喺同一個空間三年"},{"pid":"07ea8af75a0fb4c75d1cefedb23993010bc29de1","tid":2409780,"uid":76600,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T05:54:11.000Z","msg":"份工返庇護工場織籐籃？"},{"pid":"76d1113eb79ce5cbe7688805fa71cc65d5cd42d6","tid":2409780,"uid":292624,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"f2fb0631b87f768c2dad9b973efaf3a49e3c91c1","tid":2409780,"uid":140956,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"quote":{"pid":"f9856ea754740f2794ff5cc8ab65e665015922d4","tid":2409780,"uid":292624,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"quote":{"pid":"12aa87217894a6abdf95a540aa962e6d23593677","tid":2409780,"uid":140956,"like":68,"dislike":1,"score":67,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T05:49:43.000Z","msg":"毒撚界既恥辱<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n喊曬衝出門口咁誇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T05:50:31.000Z","msg":"真人真事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇到我眼都突埋<br />\n同事話佢地見慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"ci