rmal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後好鍾意郁啲就挨到勁埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />講野又有口氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />心諗點解咁大陣味，點知佢一除罩食飯先睇到佢啲牙係黑黃色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />問過佢 佢話自己無食煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁即係唔刷牙？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有坐佢附近食飯真係地獄黎 食野&lsquo;&lsquo;jap jap&rsquo;&rsquo;聲 個口唔識合埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為公司細，食飯又無人會講野，又無開冷氣，所以係靜到有蚊快過都聽到<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />識過提佢 佢話「毒撚係咁架啦」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋佢返工真係好撚鍾意放屁 由返工放到收工，前面講過公司成日好靜，佢又坐係個位到係咁放<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />連環放仲要一下放勁長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我坐附近真係勁難頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住就勁啦 有一日佢比老細鬧，當住同事面前，然後佢竟然大叫喊哂衝左出門口<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之後又死死氣返黎繼續做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n平時溝通已經勁難頂，佢仲好鍾意話自己勁鍾意初音，成屋都係佢啲公仔、海報、碟，仲話要同佢結婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n樣樣野都勁惡頂，問過原來佢係到做左三年幾四年 點解公司啲同事會頂得住<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T05:49:43.000Z","msg":"毒撚界既恥辱<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n喊曬衝出門口咁誇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T05:50:31.000Z","msg":"真人真事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇到我眼都突埋<br />\n同事話佢地見慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T13:56:29.000Z","msg":"屌你老母啊 洗唔撚洗咁樣唱鳩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85166272cab0e6537240ff5ad46fdf94a160446c","tid":2409780,"uid":34093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T13:58:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/7/7c/E29c0f03f57a26d7cfe8d920722d23ce.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20070703200119\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F7%2F7c%2FE29c0f03f57a26d7cfe8d920722d23ce.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20070703200119&h=6ccc0850&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c40f24642f32237fb63c1ac660268c899cde2220","tid":2409780,"uid":212168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T13:59:20.000Z","msg":"呢d真心劇毒"},{"pid":"2301d390ee12a67e0ecfdd28d299b1a64c05ea50","tid":2409780,"uid":292624,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c40f24642f32237fb63c1ac660268c899cde2220","tid":2409780,"uid":212168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T13:59:20.000Z","msg":"呢d真